body: "## Charter\nLiving capability epic for docs, onboarding, release, and CI health: docs/ tree accuracy, docs-skills-gate link validation, CHANGELOG generation (pm-changelog), daily date-based auto-release, CI Gates (static + coverage + windows-regression + nightly), and contributor onboarding.\n\n## Scope\n- In: docs freshness gates, changelog:pm:check drift gate, auto-release workflow (RELEASE_PAT, Sentry gate), nightly matrix failures, coverage gate (100% literal all-src per ADR pm-w13j).\n- Out: telemetry/Sentry runtime behavior (pm-5oj5), code-quality ratchets (pm-92if).\n\n## Standing invariants\n- CHANGELOG is fully auto-generated from CLOSED items; regen is the LAST step of any change (updated_at bucketing trap).\n- NEVER change package.json version manually; releases are date-based (2026.<month>.<day>) cut by the daily workflow.\n- windows-regression job is the oracle for Windows path/shebang issues.\n\n## Open children (2026-07-04)\n- pm-7zs0 — recurring reminder: verify daily auto-release tagged AND advanced npm latest.\n- pm-lt6n — GH-427 Windows Node 24 nightly: POSIX-only error-code assertions (in progress).\n- pm-esbt — docs-skills-gate: validate anchor fragments in relative links."
